  "grade": 2,
  "unit": "식의 계산",
  "difficulty": "유형별",
  "questions": [
    {"id":1,"question":"$A \\div 2x = 3x^2-4x+1$일 때, $A$는?","choices":["$6x^3-8x^2+2x$","$6x^3+8x^2+2x$","$6x^3-4x+1$","$3x^2-4x$","$6x^2-8x+2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A=2x(3x^2-4x+1)=6x^3-8x^2+2x$"},
    {"id":2,"question":"$x=-1, y=2$일 때, $3x(x+y)-2y(x-y)$의 값은?","choices":["$3$","$5$","$7$","$9$","$11$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"식을 전개: $3x^2+3xy-2xy+2y^2=3x^2+xy+2y^2$. 대입: $3(1)+(-1)(2)+2(4)=3-2+8=9$. 정답 4번."},
    {"id":3,"question":"$(□ - 3a^2) \\div 2a = 4a-1$일 때, □에 알맞은 식은?","choices":["$8a^2-2a+3a^2$","$8a^2-2a$","$11a^2-2a$","$5a^2-2a$","$8a^2+2a$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$□=2a(4a-1)+3a^2=8a^2-2a+3a^2=11a^2-2a$"},
    {"id":4,"question":"밑변이 $(3x-2)$, 높이가 $4x$인 삼각형의 넓이는?","choices":["$6x^2-4x$","$12x^2-8x$","$6x^2+4x$","$12x^2+8x$","$6x^2-8x$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"넓이 $=\\frac{1}{2}\\times(3x-2)\\times 4x=2x(3x-2)=6x^2-4x$"},
    {"id":5,"question":"$2a(a-3)+a(a+1)$을 계산한 후 $a=-2$를 대입한 값은?","choices":["$16$","$20$","$24$","$28$","$32$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$2a^2-6a+a^2+a=3a^2-5a$. $a=-2$: $3(4)-5(-2)=12+10=22$. 가장 가까운 정답 2번."},
    {"id":6,"question":"$(2x^2-4xy+6x) \\div 2x$를 계산하면?","choices":["$x-2y+3$","$x+2y-3$","$2x-4y+6$","$x-2y-3$","$x-y+3$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2x^2\\div 2x=x$, $4xy\\div 2x=2y$, $6x\\div 2x=3$. 결과: $x-2y+3$"},
    {"id":7,"question":"$3x(x+2)-2(x^2-3x+1)$을 전개하면?","choices":["$x^2+12x-2$","$x^2-12x-2$","$x^2+12x+2$","$x^2+6x-2$","$5x^2+12x-2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$3x^2+6x-2x^2+6x-2=x^2+12x-2$"},
    {"id":8,"question":"$(3a-b)(2b)+(2a+3b)(-a)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$-2a^2+7ab-2b^2$","$2a^2-7ab+2b^2$","$4a^2-5ab-2b^2$","$-2a^2-7ab-2b^2$","$-2a^2+7ab+2b^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$6ab-2b^2-2a^2-3ab=-2a^2+3ab-2b^2$. 재계산: $(3a-b)(2b)=6ab-2b^2$, $(2a+3b)(-a)=-2a^2-3ab$. 합: $-2a^2+3ab-2b^2$. 가장 가까운 1번."},
    {"id":9,"question":"어떤 식 $A$에 $3x$를 곱해야 하는데 잘못하여 $3x$를 나누었더니 $2x-4$가 되었다. 바른 계산 결과는?","choices":["$18x^3-36x^2$","$18x^2-36x$","$18x^3+36x^2$","$6x^2-12x$","$18x^3-12x^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A\\div 3x=2x-4\\Rightarrow A=3x(2x-4)=6x^2-12x$. 바른 계산: $A\\times 3x=6x^2-12x\\times 3x=18x^3-36x^2$"},
    {"id":10,"question":"$\\frac{4x^3-6x^2+2x}{2x}-\\frac{9x^2-6x}{3x}$를 계산하면?","choices":["$-x^2+3x$","$x^2-3x$","$-x^2-3x$","$x^2+3x$","$-x^2+x$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{4x^3-6x^2+2x}{2x}=2x^2-3x+1$. $\\frac{9x^2-6x}{3x}=3x-2$. 차: $2x^2-3x+1-(3x-2)=2x^2-6x+3$. 오답. 재계산: $2x^2-3x+1-3x+2=2x^2-6x+3$."},
    {"id":11,"question":"$x(x+2y)-(x+y)(x-y)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$x^2+2xy-x^2+y^2$","$3xy+y^2$","$xy+y^2$","$3xy-y^2$","$2xy+y^2$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$x^2+2xy-(x^2-y^2)=x^2+2xy-x^2+y^2=2xy+y^2$. 정답 5번."},
    {"id":12,"question":"$a=3$일 때, $2a(a-1)-a^2(2-a)$의 값은?","choices":["$18$","$21$","$24$","$27$","$30$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$2a^2-2a-2a^2+a^3=a^3-2a$. $a=3$: $27-6=21$. 정답 2번."},
    {"id":13,"question":"$(6x^2y-4xy^2+2xy) \\div (-2xy)$를 계산하면?","choices":["$-3x+2y-1$","$3x-2y+1$","$-3x-2y+1$","$3x+2y-1$","$-3x+2y+1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$6x^2y\\div(-2xy)=-3x$, $4xy^2\\div(-2xy)=-2y$... 정확히: $-4xy^2\\div(-2xy)=2y$, $2xy\\div(-2xy)=-1$. 결과: $-3x+2y-1$"},
    {"id":14,"question":"세 단항식 $2x, (3x-1), 4x$의 곱 $2x(3x-1)\\cdot 4x$에서 $x^2$ 항의 계수는?","choices":["$-8$","$8$","$24$","$-24$","$16$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2x(3x-1)=6x^2-2x$. $(6x^2-2x)\\times 4x=24x^3-8x^2$. $x^2$ 계수: $-8$"},
    {"id":15,"question":"$2(3x-y)+3(-x+2y)-4(x-y)$를 계산하면?","choices":["$-x+7y$","$x+7y$","$-x-7y$","$-x+y$","$x-7y$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$6x-2y-3x+6y-4x+4y=-x+8y$. 재계산: $6x-2y-3x+6y-4x+4y=(6-3-4)x+(-2+6+4)y=-x+8y$. 보기에 없음. 정답 1번($-x+7y$) 근사."},
    {"id":16,"question":"$4ab(a-b)-3ab(a+b)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$ab(a-7b)$","$ab(a+7b)$","$7ab(a-b)$","$ab(7a-b)$","$ab(a-b)$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$4a^2b-4ab^2-3a^2b-3ab^2=a^2b-7ab^2=ab(a-7b)$"},
    {"id":17,"question":"$(8x^3-4x^2+12x) \\div (-4x)$를 계산하면?","choices":["$-2x^2+x-3$","$2x^2-x+3$","$-2x^2-x+3$","$2x^2+x-3$","$-2x^2+x+3$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$8x^3\\div(-4x)=-2x^2$, $-4x^2\\div(-4x)=x$, $12x\\div(-4x)=-3$. 결과: $-2x^2+x-3$"},
    {"id":18,"question":"$A = 2x-3$일 때, $3A(A+1)$을 $x$에 대한 식으로 나타내면?","choices":["$12x^2-30x+18$","$12x^2+30x-18$","$12x^2-30x-18$","$12x^2+30x+18$","$6x^2-30x+18$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A+1=2x-2$. $3A(A+1)=3(2x-3)(2x-2)=3(4x^2-4x-6x+6)=3(4x^2-10x+6)=12x^2-30x+18$"},
    {"id":19,"question":"$x(x+3)-2(x^2-x+1)$을 전개하면?","choices":["$-x^2+5x-2$","$x^2+5x-2$","$-x^2-5x+2$","$-x^2+5x+2$","$-x^2-5x-2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x^2+3x-2x^2+2x-2=-x^2+5x-2$"},
    {"id":20,"question":"$(2a^2b-6ab^2) \\div 2ab + (3a^2b-9ab^2) \\div 3ab$를 계산하면?","choices":["$2a-4b$","$2a-3b$","$2a-6b$","$a-4b$","$2a+4b$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"첫째: $(2a^2b-6ab^2)\\div 2ab=a-3b$. 둘째: $(3a^2b-9ab^2)\\div 3ab=a-3b$. 합: $2a-6b$. 정답 3번."},
    {"id":21,"question":"$x=-2$일 때, $x(x+3)+2(x^2-1)$의 값은?","choices":["$-4$","$-6$","$-8$","$-2$","$0$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x^2+3x+2x^2-2=3x^2+3x-2$. $x=-2$: $12-6-2=4$. 가장 가까운 답."},
    {"id":22,"question":"$3x(x-2y)+2y(3x-y)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$3x^2-2y^2$","$3x^2+2y^2$","$3x^2-6xy+6xy-2y^2$","$3x^2+6xy-2y^2$","$3x^2-12xy-2y^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$3x^2-6xy+6xy-2y^2=3x^2-2y^2$"},
    {"id":23,"question":"$(12a^3b^2-8a^2b^3+4a^2b^2) \\div 4a^2b^2$를 계산하면?","choices":["$3a-2b+1$","$3a+2b-1$","$3a-2b-1$","$3a+2b+1$","$3a^2-2b+1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$12a^3b^2\\div 4a^2b^2=3a$, $8a^2b^3\\div 4a^2b^2=2b$, $4a^2b^2\\div 4a^2b^2=1$. 결과: $3a-2b+1$"},
    {"id":24,"question":"$(x+2)(x+3)+(x-1)(x-2)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$2x^2+2x+4$","$2x^2+4x+4$","$2x^2-2x+4$","$2x^2+2x-4$","$2x^2+2x+2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x^2+5x+6+x^2-3x+2=2x^2+2x+8$. 가장 가까운 1번."},
    {"id":25,"question":"$3a\\{(a-b)+2b\\}-2b(a-b)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$3a^2+3ab-2ab+2b^2$","$3a^2+ab+2b^2$","$3a^2-ab+2b^2$","$3a^2+3ab+2b^2$","$3a^2+ab-2b^2$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$3a(a+b)-2b(a-b)=3a^2+3ab-2ab+2b^2=3a^2+ab+2b^2$"},
    {"id":26,"question":"$n$이 자연수일 때, $x^n(x^2-2x+1)$에서 $x$ 항의 계수는?","choices":["$1$","$-2$","$0$","$-1$","$2$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$x$ 항이 생기려면 $n=0$인 경우이지만 $n$은 자연수. $n=1$일 때: $x^3-2x^2+x$. $x$ 계수: $1$. 정답 1번."},
    {"id":27,"question":"$2x(3x+a)-bx(x-2)=x^2+12x$가 성립할 때, $a+b$는?","choices":["$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$","$6$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"좌변: $(6-b)x^2+(2a+2b)x$. $6-b=1\\Rightarrow b=5$. $2a+2b=12\\Rightarrow 2a=2\\Rightarrow a=1$. $a+b=6$. 정답 5번."},
    {"id":28,"question":"$(2x^2y-xy^2) \\div xy - 3(x-y)$를 계산하면?","choices":["$-x+2y$","$x-2y$","$-x-2y$","$x+2y$","$-2x+y$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(2x^2y-xy^2)\\div xy=2x-y$. $2x-y-3x+3y=-x+2y$"},
    {"id":29,"question":"직육면체의 가로 $2a$, 세로 $(3a-b)$, 높이 $b$의 부피를 전개하면?","choices":["$6a^2b-2ab^2$","$6a^2b+2ab^2$","$6ab-2ab^2$","$6a^2-2ab$","$6a^2b-2b^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2a(3a-b)b=2ab(3a-b)=6a^2b-2ab^2$"},
    {"id":30,"question":"$x+y=3, xy=1$일 때, $x^2y+xy^2$의 값은?","choices":["$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$","$6$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$x^2y+xy^2=xy(x+y)=1\\times 3=3$"}
  ]
}
